{"tid":1173710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普再開嗆：美國還沒準備好與支那達成貿易協議","createTime":"2019-05-27T10:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T10:31:54.000Z","uid":32511,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1c7d48633b49703da782711c529ab7f522bb69","tid":1173710,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普27日在日本進行國是訪問時表示，美國還沒準備好與中國達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n川普在東京與日本首相安倍晉三舉行聯合記者會時表示：「我想他們現在可能希望達成他們原本試著重新談判前，就已在檯面上的協議。他們想達成協議，我們還沒準備好達成協議。」<br />\n<br />\n川普表示，美國對中國產品實施的關稅「可能非常大幅、非常輕易地上調」。此前，美中雙方的貿易協商已於本月稍早觸礁，兩國責怪彼此，而川普已威脅要再課徵更多關稅。<br />\n<br />\n不過川普仍對美中最終將達成協議表達樂觀看法。他說：「我認為在未來某個時候，中國與美國肯定將有個很棒的貿易協議，我們拭目以待。」"},{"pid":"c209009fb1f4a7ac99faeab2245e6da7f6c4be8c","tid":1173710,"uid":217336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"8ea79b1de55a5d475d43c2fe6d7095fde45ee18d","tid":1173710,"uid":20066,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:04:53.000Z","msg":"美方自知沒有條件與中方談判<br />\n<br />\n中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7e9dae8ce235ea6379092e75a537b9630bea0c","tid":1173710,"uid":43428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"隔一兩星期又會話準備好同支那準備達成協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd86ea5ed163651e0311f85bb59b4b8133bb95e","tid":1173710,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"到你想達成，又話未係時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e360e98ae236371a430058994977ccc1d40a128","tid":1173710,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed7e9dae8ce235ea6379092e75a537b9630bea0c","tid":1173710,"uid":43428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T